    { question: "What exactly is AI phone answering for alarm installers?", answer: "AI phone answering for alarm installers is a call handling system that captures security-related enquiries professionally even when you\'re on a ladder wiring a PIR sensor or programming a panel in a customer\'s hallway. Security calls often come from people in a heightened emotional state — they\'ve been burgled, their neighbour has been broken into, or they\'ve just moved to a new area and feel vulnerable. The AI recognises this and responds with appropriate reassurance while capturing the details you need: property type, number of entry points, whether they want CCTV alongside an alarm, their budget expectations, and when they\'d like the installation done. For existing customers calling about false alarms, system faults, or zone issues, the AI captures the alarm system model, which zones are affected, and error codes displayed on the panel. Every call produces a detailed lead summary delivered to your phone immediately." },
